### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/health
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Create Payment Session
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/create-session
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "order_id": "order_001_{{ $timestamp }}",
  "amount": 100.50,
  "currency": "INR",
  "customer_id": "customer_001",
  "customer_name": "John Doe",
  "customer_email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "customer_phone": "+919876543210",
  "description": "Test payment for order",
  "return_url": "https://your-domain.com/payment/success",
  "notify_url": "https://your-domain.com/api/v1/webhook/cashfree"
}

###

### Verify Payment
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "order_id": "order_001_1672531200"
}

###

### Get Payment Details
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/order_001_1672531200
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Refund Payment
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/order_001_1672531200/refund
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 50.25,
  "reason": "Customer requested refund"
}

###

### Cancel Payment
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/order_001_1672531200/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Create Split Settlement
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/order_001_1672531200/split
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "splits": [
    {
      "vendor_id": "vendor_001",
      "amount": 70.00
    },
    {
      "vendor_id": "vendor_002",
      "percentage": 30.0
    }
  ]
}

###

### Get Settlement Details
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/settlements/settlement_001
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get Refund Details
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/refunds/refund_001
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get All Payments (with pagination)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments?limit=10&offset=0
Content-Type: application/json

